flowchart TD
    A([User sends /register]) --> B{Already registered?}
    B -->|No| C[Send upload prompt]
    B -->|Yes| D[Send re-upload prompt<br/>upsert will replace existing]
    C & D --> E[Wait for document]

    E --> F{Valid format?<br/>PDF / DOC / DOCX}
    F -->|No| G[Send format error] --> E
    F -->|Yes| H[Send processing message]

    H --> I[parser.extract_text]
    I --> J{Extraction OK?}
    J -->|Empty text| K[Send error: unreadable file] --> E
    J -->|OK| L[extractor.extract_profile_fields via LLM]

    L --> M{LLM response valid JSON?}
    M -->|No or error| N[Send error message] --> E
    M -->|Yes| O[embedder.embed_profile]

    O --> P[Show profile preview card]
    P --> Q{User confirms?}
    Q -->|No / re-upload| E
    Q -->|/cancel| R([End cancelled])
    Q -->|Yes| S{Existing profile?}

    S -->|Yes upsert| T[Delete old Weaviate object<br/>Overwrite MinIO file]
    S -->|No insert| U[Fresh insert path]
    T & U --> V[mongo_client.upsert_user]
    V --> W[weaviate_client.upsert_member_profile]
    W --> X[minio_client.upload_resume]
    X --> Y[Send success message]
    Y --> Z([End])
